The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | Akademi
                                                                                                               Akademi
                            
	New Delhi, Feb. 20: Sunil Gangopadhyay was today elected president of the Sahitya Akademi. The writer from Bengal got 45 votes against 40 bagged by his friend from Kerala, M.T. Vasudevan Nair.                                                                                                                                                                            
